{
  "id": "69e45d21818d66303e6764b5",
  "title": "1年カレンダーの隣接日付に昨日明日だけじゃなくて一週間前後と一ヶ月前後を追加するのはどうだろう",
  "created": 1776573730,
  "updated": 1776588512,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e45d21818d66303e6764b5",
      "text": "1年カレンダーの隣接日付に昨日明日だけじゃなくて一週間前後と一ヶ月前後を追加するのはどうだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776573730
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe250",
      "text": "from [2026/04/19]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776573730
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d260000000000dbe26e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573734,
      "updated": 1776573734
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe252",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776573730
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe253",
      "text": " [1年カレンダー]の隣接日付に昨日明日だけじゃなくて一週間前後と一ヶ月前後を追加するのはどうだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776573730
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe254",
      "text": " \t昨日 ← 今日 → 明日",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776573730
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe255",
      "text": " \t先週 ← 今日 → 来週",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776573730
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe256",
      "text": " \t先月 ← 今日 → 来月",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776573730
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe257",
      "text": " \t週はともかく月がなぁ。31日と30日、28日と29日がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776573730
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe258",
      "text": " \t閏年と同じ分岐でいいか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776573730
    },
    {
      "id": "69e478750000000000dbe385",
      "text": " \t\tcode:mermaid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776580726,
      "updated": 1776580726
    },
    {
      "id": "69e478750000000000dbe386",
      "text": " \t\t graph",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776580726,
      "updated": 1776580726
    },
    {
      "id": "69e478750000000000dbe387",
      "text": " \t\t subgraph 閏日",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776580726,
      "updated": 1776580726
    },
    {
      "id": "69e478750000000000dbe388",
      "text": " \t\t a(2/28)-->b(2/29)-->c(3/1)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776580726,
      "updated": 1776580726
    },
    {
      "id": "69e478750000000000dbe389",
      "text": " \t\t a-->c",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776580726,
      "updated": 1776580726
    },
    {
      "id": "69e478750000000000dbe38a",
      "text": " \t\t end",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776580726,
      "updated": 1776580726
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe259",
      "text": " \t\tcode:mermaid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776580726
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe25a",
      "text": " \t\t graph LR",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776580745
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45d210000000000dbe25b",
      "text": " \t\t d(12/28); e(12/29); f(12/30); g(12/31);",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573730,
      "updated": 1776580734
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463610000000000dbe33d",
      "text": " \t\t d-->1/28-->2/28-->3/28-->4/28-->5/28-->6/28-->7/28-->8/28-->9/28-->10/28-->11/28-->12/28",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575329,
      "updated": 1776575329
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463a50000000000dbe36a",
      "text": " \t\t 1/29-->2/28",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575397,
      "updated": 1776575397
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463a50000000000dbe36b",
      "text": " \t\t 1/30-->2/28",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575397,
      "updated": 1776575397
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463a50000000000dbe36c",
      "text": " \t\t 1/31-->2/28",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575397,
      "updated": 1776575397
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463610000000000dbe33e",
      "text": " \t\t e-->1/29-->2/29-->3/29-->4/29-->5/29-->6/29-->7/29-->8/29-->9/29-->10/29-->11/29-->12/29",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575329,
      "updated": 1776575329
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463a90000000000dbe371",
      "text": " \t\t 1/30-->2/29",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575401,
      "updated": 1776575401
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463a90000000000dbe372",
      "text": " \t\t 1/31-->2/29",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575401,
      "updated": 1776575401
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463ac0000000000dbe377",
      "text": " \t\t 1/29-->3/29",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575404,
      "updated": 1776575404
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463ac0000000000dbe378",
      "text": " \t\t 2/28-->3/29",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575404,
      "updated": 1776575404
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463610000000000dbe33f",
      "text": " \t\t f-->1/30--->3/30-->4/30-->5/30-->6/30-->7/30-->8/30-->9/30-->10/30-->11/30-->12/30",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575329,
      "updated": 1776575329
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463b00000000000dbe37b",
      "text": " \t\t 2/28-->3/30",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575408,
      "updated": 1776575408
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463b00000000000dbe37c",
      "text": " \t\t 2/29-->3/30",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575408,
      "updated": 1776575408
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463610000000000dbe340",
      "text": " \t\t 3/31-->4/30-->5/31-->6/30-->7/31; 8/31-->9/30-->10/31-->11/30-->12/31;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575329,
      "updated": 1776575329
    },
    {
      "id": "69e463610000000000dbe341",
      "text": " \t\t g-->1/31--->3/31--->5/31--->7/31-->8/31--->10/31--->12/31",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575329,
      "updated": 1776575329
    },
    {
      "id": "69e462d10000000000dbe299",
      "text": " \t\t 2/28-->3/31",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575185,
      "updated": 1776575193
    },
    {
      "id": "69e462d90000000000dbe29a",
      "text": " \t\t 2/29-->3/31",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776575194,
      "updated": 1776575199
    },
    {
      "id": "69e45da80000000000dbe26f",
      "text": "\t\t\t2 月前後がヒドイ事になっている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776573864,
      "updated": 1776580785
    },
    {
      "id": "69e478b20000000000dbe38c",
      "text": "\t\t30 日、31 日で隣接させて満遍なく散らすのはどうだろう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776580786,
      "updated": 1776586290
    },
    {
      "id": "69e478f90000000000dbe38d",
      "text": "\t\tcode:mermaid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776580857,
      "updated": 1776581000
    },
    {
      "id": "69e479050000000000dbe38e",
      "text": "\t\t graph LR",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776581000,
      "updated": 1776581000
    },
    {
      "id": "69e485c80000000000dbe582",
      "text": "\t\t ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776584137,
      "updated": 1776584137
    },
    {
      "id": "69e48d530000000000dbe5cc",
      "text": "   1/1-->1/31 & 2/1;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776586067,
      "updated": 1776586067
    },
    {
      "id": "69e48d540000000000dbe5cd",
      "text": "   1/2-->2/1 & 2/2;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776586068,
      "updated": 1776586078
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490490000000000dbe5d9",
      "text": "   1/31-->3/1 & 3/2;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776586826,
      "updated": 1776586882
    },
    {
      "id": "69e48b350000000000dbe5ae",
      "text": "   2/1-->3/2 & 3/3;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776585526,
      "updated": 1776586773
    },
    {
      "id": "69e48d690000000000dbe5ce",
      "text": "   3/1-->3/31 & 4/1;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776586090,
      "updated": 1776586090
    },
    {
      "id": "69e48d690000000000dbe5cf",
      "text": "   3/2-->4/1 & 4/2;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776586090,
      "updated": 1776586100
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490500000000000dbe5db",
      "text": "   3/31-->4/30 & 5/1;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776586832,
      "updated": 1776586832
    },
    {
      "id": "69e48a480000000000dbe5a2",
      "text": "   4/1-->5/1 & 5/2;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776585782,
      "updated": 1776586090
    },
